body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for contacting CarMart Support. My name is Edward Turner. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hello, my name is Rose Hall.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Rose. How can I assist you today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I need to return an item, but I'm unsure of the process.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I can help with that. Could you please provide me with your order number?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, the order number is three five six eight nine.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Rose. Additionally, for security purposes, could you confirm your date of birth in the format day, month, year?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: My date of birth is nine zero eight, June, one nine seven five.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Great, thank you for verifying. Is there anything else I can assist you with today, Rose?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: No, that's all. Thank you for your help.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: You're welcome, Rose. Should you have any more questions, feel free to reach out. Have a wonderful day.
